<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Henry Shop</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:Arial;
background:#f5f5f5;
}

/* TOP BAR */

.topbar{
background:#ffcc00;
padding:10px;
display:flex;
justify-content:flex-end;
gap:20px;
font-weight:bold;
}

/* COVER */

.cover{
height:300px;
background:url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505740420928-5e560c06d30e") center/cover;
position:relative;
}

.avatar{
width:160px;
height:160px;
border-radius:50%;
border:6px solid white;
position:absolute;
bottom:-80px;
left:50%;
transform:translateX(-50%);
}

/* SOCIAL LEFT */

.social{
position:fixed;
top:200px;
left:0;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
}

.social a{
padding:15px;
color:white;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

.fb{background:#1877f2;}
.yt{background:#ff0000;}
.tt{background:black;}
.ig{background:#e1306c;}

/* PRODUCTS */

.products{
margin-top:120px;
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
gap:20px;
padding:40px;
}

.product{
background:white;
padding:15px;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
text-align:center;
}

.product img{
width:100%;
border-radius:10px;
}

.price{
color:red;
font-size:20px;
}

.old{
text-decoration:line-through;
color:gray;
font-size:14px;
}

/* CHAT */

.chat{
position:fixed;
bottom:20px;
right:20px;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:10px;
}

.chat a{
background:#25D366;
color:white;
padding:12px 16px;
border-radius:8px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:bold;
}

.webchat{
background:#0084ff;
}

/* FOOTER */

footer{
background:#222;
color:white;
padding:40px;
margin-top:50px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="topbar">
🔍 Tìm kiếm | 🛒 Giỏ hàng | 🔔 Thông báo | 👤 Đăng nhập
</div>

<div class="cover">
<img class="avatar" src="https://i.imgur.com/2DhmtJ4.png">
</div>

<div class="social">
<a class="fb" href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
<a class="yt" href="https://youtube.com" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
<a class="tt" href="https://tiktok.com" target="_blank">TikTok</a>
<a class="ig" href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
</div>

<div class="products">

<div class="product">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511707171634-5f897ff02aa9">
<h3>Iphone 15</h3>
<div class="price">19.990.000₫</div>
<div class="old">22.990.000₫</div>
⭐ 4.8 | Đã bán 320
</div>

<div class="product">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580910051074-3eb694886505">
<h3>Tai nghe Bluetooth</h3>
<div class="price">690.000₫</div>
<div class="old">990.000₫</div>
⭐ 4.7 | Đã bán 150
</div>

<div class="product">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585386959984-a41552231658">
<h3>Loa Bluetooth</h3>
<div class="price">1.200.000₫</div>
<div class="old">1.500.000₫</div>
⭐ 4.9 | Đã bán 210
</div>

<div class="product">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517336714731-489689fd1ca8">
<h3>Laptop Gaming</h3>
<div class="price">24.500.000₫</div>
<div class="old">27.000.000₫</div>
⭐ 4.8 | Đã bán 98
</div>

</div>

<div class="chat">
<a href="https://zalo.me" target="_blank">Chat Zalo</a>
<a class="webchat" href="#">Chat Web</a>
</div>

<footer>

<h3>Henry Shop</h3>

📍 Địa chỉ: Hà Nội, Việt Nam  
☎ Tổng đài: 1900 0000  
📧 Gmail: henryshop@gmail.com  

<br><br>

<h4>Đối tác & nhà tài trợ</h4>
Apple | Samsung | Sony | Xiaomi

</footer>

</body>
</html>
